{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18144590-the-alchemist", "title": "The Alchemist", "titleComplete": "The Alchemist", "description": "Combining magic, mysticism, wisdom, and wonder into an inspiring tale of self-discovery, The Alchemist has become a modern classic, selling millions of copies around the world and transforming the lives of countless readers across generations.Paulo Coelho's masterpiece tells the mystical story of Santiago, an Andalusian shepherd boy who yearns to travel in search of a worldly treasure. His quest will lead him to riches far different\u2014and far more satisfying\u2014than he ever imagined. Santiago's journey teaches us about the essential wisdom of listening to our hearts, recognizing opportunity and learning to read the omens strewn along life's path, and, most importantly, following our dreams.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1654371463i/18144590.jpg", "genres": ["Self Help", "Fiction", "Adventure", "Fantasy", "Novels", "Spirituality", "Philosophy", "Classics", "Audiobook", "Literature"], "asin": "0062315005", "isbn": "0062315005", "isbn13": "9780062315007", "publisher": "HarperOne", "author": ["Paulo Coelho"], "publishDate": 1397545200000, "characters": ["Alchemist", "Melchizedek", "Santiago"], "places": ["North Africa", "Tangier", "Egypt", "Andalusia", "Morocco", "Sahara Desert", "Spain"], "ratingHistogram": [134750, 237646, 588206, 875232, 1191758], "ratingsCount": 3027592, "reviewsCount": 119256, "numPages": 182, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "NBDB National Book Awards", "awardedAt": 1420099200000, "category": "Translation", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Grand Prix des lectrices de Elle", "awardedAt": 788947200000, "category": "roman", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Premio Grinzane Cavour", "awardedAt": 820483200000, "category": "Narrativa Straniera", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Corine Internationaler Buchpreis", "awardedAt": 1009872000000, "cat